岩田聰在任期间接下来的游戏硬件，包括[[任天堂3DS|任天堂3DS]]和[[Wii_U|Wii U]]在内，市场表现都没有任天堂DS和Wii好。任天堂的收入也在2010年後开始下滑<ref name="Finances2012"/><ref name="Profitable2015"/>。任天堂3DS是一台拥有[[裸眼3D|裸眼3D]]功能的掌机，玩家不需要佩戴任何东西便可以看到3D效果。在开发任天堂3DS的新机型[[新任天堂3DS|新任天堂3DS]]时，他曾命令硬件工程师在开发末期加入新的硬件功能。岩田聰称，他的技术背景得以让他有效控制任天堂的硬件工程师，不被他们欺骗<ref name="Time2015"/>。任天堂对3DS寄予厚望，希望它作为任天堂DS的后继机种能够给收入开始疲软的公司注入新的活力<ref>{{cite news|first=Juro|last=Osawa|newspaper=[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]|publisher=[[道琼斯公司|道琼斯公司]]|date=2011-01-10|access-date=2015-09-03|title=Nintendo's chief defends 3DS|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052748704030704576071000866318220|archive-date=2016-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160222152537/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052748704030704576071000866318220|dead-url=no|language=en|subscription=yes}}</ref>。不过，任天堂3DS在上市初期的市场表现不佳，任天堂在2011年7月29日当天股票狂跌12%<ref>{{cite news|first=Kazuyo|last=Sawa|agency=[[彭博新聞社|彭博新聞社]]|publisher=[[彭博新聞社|彭博新聞社]]|date=2011-07-29|access-date=2015-09-02|title=Nintendo stock rout costs Yamauchi $300 million in one day|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2011-07-29/nintendo-s-yamauchi-loses-500-million-in-single-day-after-plunge-in-stock|archive-date=2017-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170912055200/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2011-07-29/nintendo-s-yamauchi-loses-500-million-in-single-day-after-plunge-in-stock|dead-url=no|language=en|subscription=yes}}</ref>。任天堂只得宣布3DS在当年8月降价：在日本从25,000日圆降至15,000日圆<ref>{{Cite web|title=Nintendo announces huge 3DS price cut|url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-07-28-nintendo-announces-3ds-price-cut|accessdate=2021-03-19|date=2011-07-28|last=Yin-Poole|first=Wesley|work=Eurogamer|language=en}}</ref>，在北美从250美元降至170美元<ref>{{cite news|first=Nathan|last=Olivarez-Giles|newspaper=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|publisher=Tribune Publishing|date=2011-07-28|access-date=2015-09-03|title=Nintendo 3DS price dropping to $170|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/technology/2011/07/nintendo-3ds-price-discount.html|archive-date=2017-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170614055626/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/technology/2011/07/nintendo-3ds-price-discount.html|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。不过，任天堂3DS的销量仍长期低于预期<ref>{{cite news|newspaper=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]|publisher=[[電訊媒體集團|電訊媒體集團]]|date=2012-10-24|access-date=2015-09-03|title=Nintendo suffers ahead of Wii U launch|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/nintendo/9630995/Nintendo-suffers-ahead-of-Wii-U-launch.html|archive-date=2015-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926072356/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/nintendo/9630995/Nintendo-suffers-ahead-of-Wii-U-launch.html|dead-url=no|language=en|subscription=yes}}</ref>。岩田聰后来在2014年承认他当时错误预估市场形势，在Wii发售后未能妥善处理人们生活方式的转变<ref name="WSJ011714">{{cite news|first1=Mayumi|last1=Negishi|first2=Hiroyuki|last2=Kachi|first3=Ian|last3=Sherr|newspaper=[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]|publisher=[[道琼斯公司|道琼斯公司]]|date=2014-01-17|access-date=2015-09-03|title=Nintendo sees loss on dismal Wii U sales|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052702303465004579325760899958956|archive-date=2016-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160222161556/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052702303465004579325760899958956|dead-url=no|language=en|subscription=yes}}</ref>——在家庭游戏人气下滑的时候仍然关注于家庭游戏<ref name="BB012114"/>。

2012年末<!--欧美是11月中下旬，日本是12月初，因而模糊至2012年末-->发售的Wii U<ref>{{cite magazine|last=Ewalt|first=David M.|date=2012-09-13|title=Nintendo Reveals Wii U Launch Date, Price, Details|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/davidewalt/2012/09/13/nintendo-reveals-wii-u-launch-date-price-details/|dead-url=no|magazine=[[福布斯|福布斯]]|language=en|publisher=福布斯公司|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170925084156/https://www.forbes.com/sites/davidewalt/2012/09/13/nintendo-reveals-wii-u-launch-date-price-details/|archive-date=2017-09-25|access-date=2015-09-03}}</ref>被任天堂以亏本价发售。任天堂希望这能带动软件销量，以缓解公司的亏损状况<ref>{{cite news|first=Kyle|last=Orland|newspaper=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|publisher=[[康泰纳仕|康泰纳仕]]|date=2012-10-25|access-date=2015-09-03|title=Why Nintendo is losing money on each Wii U launch unit|url=https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2012/10/why-nintendo-is-losing-money-on-each-wii-u-launch-unit/|archive-date=2017-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170708061018/https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2012/10/why-nintendo-is-losing-money-on-each-wii-u-launch-unit/|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。Wii U与Wii相比，新增了对[[高清画面|高清画面]]的支持，但这却给开发团队带去了意想不到的困难，游戏发售一推再推。索尼和微软在[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]和[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]发售初期也遇到了类似的问题，但岩田聰对这两家在内的竞争对手毫不关心，为任天堂雪上加霜<ref>{{cite web|title=Miyamoto: We underestimated cost of HD development|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2013-07-05-miyamoto-we-underestimated-cost-of-hd-development|date=2013-07-05|last=Sinclair|first=Brendan|work=GamesIndustry.biz|publisher=Gamer Network|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-09-08|archive-date=2017-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701191026/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2013-07-05-miyamoto-we-underestimated-cost-of-hd-development}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Iwata: "We don't care about what other companies are doing"|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2013-06-17-iwata-we-dont-care-about-what-other-companies-are-doing|date=2013-06-17|last=Handrahan|first=Matthew|work=GamesIndustry.biz|publisher=Gamer Network|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-09-08|archive-date=2017-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701190623/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2013-06-17-iwata-we-dont-care-about-what-other-companies-are-doing}}</ref>。《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》的保罗·塔西（{{lang-en|Paul Tassi}}）认为任天堂本应从前一个世代索尼和微软转变至高清画面的过程中吸取教训，让自己更好适应这次转变<ref>{{cite magazine|last=Tassi|first=Paul|date=2013-07-08|title=Miyamoto Admits Nintendo Underestimated the Switch to HD|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/insertcoin/2013/07/08/miyamoto-admits-nintendo-underestimated-the-switch-to-hd/|dead-url=no|magazine=[[福布斯|福布斯]]|language=en|publisher=福布斯公司|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170925084343/https://www.forbes.com/sites/insertcoin/2013/07/08/miyamoto-admits-nintendo-underestimated-the-switch-to-hd/|archive-date=2017-09-25|access-date=2015-09-08}}</ref>。Wii U最终没有达到任天堂的销量预期，成为了任天堂销售最慢的游戏平台，截至2015年6月只卖出了950万台。宫本茂将Wii U惨淡的销量归咎于大众对该主机概念和功能的误解<ref>{{cite magazine|last=Morris|first=Chris|date=2015-06-23|title=Shigeru Miyamoto: Why the Wii U crashed and burned|url=http://fortune.com/2015/06/23/shigeru-miyamoto-wii-u/|dead-url=no|magazine=[[财富_(杂志)|财富]]|language=en|publisher=[[时代公司|时代公司]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170925040004/http://fortune.com/2015/06/23/shigeru-miyamoto-wii-u/|archive-date=2017-09-25|access-date=2015-09-03|subscription=yes}}</ref>。岩田聰后来也承认Wii U作为Wii的后继机种很失败，Wii U的游戏没能展示Wii U的独特新意<ref>{{cite web|title=Nintendo: We have failed to establish Wii U as a "worthy" Wii successor|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-we-have-failed-to-establish-wii-u-as-a-worthy-wii-successor/1100-6415888/|date=2013-10-31|last=Makuch|first=Eddie|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS互動]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-09-03|archive-date=2013-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131128013158/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-we-have-failed-to-establish-wii-u-as-a-worthy-wii-successor/1100-6415888/}}</ref>。3DS和Wii U的接连失败曾让Ichiyoshi资产管理公司的秋野充成建议岩田聰辞职<ref name="BB012114">{{cite news|first1=Takashi|last1=Amano|first2=Mariko|last2=Yasu|agency=[[彭博新聞社|彭博新聞社]]|publisher=[[彭博新聞社|彭博新聞社]]|date=2014-01-21|access-date=2015-09-03|title=Nintendo's Iwata under dire after missing Wii U forecast|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2014-01-21/nintendo-s-iwata-under-fire-after-failing-to-meet-wii-u-pledge|archive-date=2017-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170912060712/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2014-01-21/nintendo-s-iwata-under-fire-after-failing-to-meet-wii-u-pledge|dead-url=no|language=en|subscription=yes}}</ref>。

任天堂的公司销售额从巅峰时期2008[[財政年度|財政年度]]（2009年3月結算）的1.8兆日圆掉至2014財政年度（2015年3月結算）的5,490亿日圆，在2011財政年度（2012年3月結算）和2013財政年度（2014年3月結算）还出现了淨利益亏损的情况<ref name="Finances2009"/><ref name="Finances2015"/>。在2010年，任天堂透露岩田聰的基础工资为6,800万日圆，但加上绩效奖金后总共达到1.87亿日圆；而宫本茂的总工资則為1亿日圆<ref>{{cite web|title=Nintendo boss earns $770,000 basic salary|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/nintendo-boss-earns-$770000-basic-salary|date=2010-06-29|last=Jenkins|first=David|work=GamesIndustry.biz|publisher=Gamer Network|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-19|archive-date=2017-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822174122/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/nintendo-boss-earns-$770000-basic-salary}}</ref>。岩田聰为公司销售额萎靡承擔責任，于2011年和2014年两度将自己的工资减半，其他董事会成员也减薪20%至30%<ref>{{cite web|title=Iwata's Salary Cut in Half, 3DS Price Drop Explained|url=http://www.1up.com/news/iwata-salary-cut-half-3ds-price-drop-explained|date=2011-07-29|last=Pereira|first=Chris|work=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|language=en|dead-url=yes|access-date=2015-07-19|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6aAMw4DwW?url=http://www.1up.com/news/iwata-salary-cut-half-3ds-price-drop-explained|archive-date=2015-07-20}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Nintendo CEO slashes salary in half to apologise for Wii U losses|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-ceo-slashes-salary-in-half-to-apologise-for-wii-u-losses/1100-6417409/|date=2014-01-29|last=Gaston|first=Martin|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS互動]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-19|archive-date=2014-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209021337/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-ceo-slashes-salary-in-half-to-apologise-for-wii-u-losses/1100-6417409/}}</ref>。为自己减薪则保障了任天堂的员工不会因公司缩减短期开支而被裁员<ref name="fun"/><ref name="73rdSH"/>。2011財政年度，任天堂遭受进入电子游戏行业30多年来第一次營業亏损<ref>{{cite magazine|last=Kain|first=Erik|date=2012-05-02|title=Nintendo Reports First Annual Loss in Three Decades, Over $500 Million in the Red|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2012/05/02/nintendo-reports-its-first-annual-loss-in-three-decades-over-500-million-in-the-red/|dead-url=no|magazine=[[福布斯|福布斯]]|language=en|publisher=福布斯公司|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170823025002/https://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2012/05/02/nintendo-reports-its-first-annual-loss-in-three-decades-over-500-million-in-the-red/|archive-date=2017-08-23|access-date=2015-09-03}}</ref>。接下来的两年任天堂连续亏损，直到2014財政年度（2015年3月結算）才勉强轉亏为盈<ref name="Finances2015"/><ref name="Profitable2015"/><ref>{{cite news|agency=[[美联社|美联社]]|newspaper=[[衛報|衛報]]|publisher=衛報媒體集團|date=2012-04-26|access-date=2015-09-03|title=Nintendo posts first loss in 30 years|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2012/apr/26/nintendo-posts-first-loss-30-years|archive-date=2017-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822181244/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2012/apr/26/nintendo-posts-first-loss-30-years|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。任天堂的業績由黑翻紅主要归功于爆款游戏《[[精靈寶可夢_歐米加紅寶石·阿爾法藍寶石|精靈寶可夢 歐米加紅寶石·阿爾法藍寶石]]》和《[[任天堂明星大亂鬥3DS/Wii_U|任天堂明星大亂鬥3DS/Wii U]]》的发售<ref name="Finances2015"/><ref name="Profitable2015">{{cite magazine|last=Luckerson|first=Victor|date=2015-05-07|title=Why Nintendo is Suddenly Profitable Again|url=http://time.com/3850264/nintendo-sales-wii-u-3ds-universal-studios/|dead-url=no|magazine=[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]|language=en|publisher=[[时代公司|时代公司]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304201209/http://time.com/3850264/nintendo-sales-wii-u-3ds-universal-studios/|archive-date=2016-03-04|access-date=2015-07-21}}</ref>。

2013年6月，岩田聰又兼任了美国任天堂的首席执行官<ref>{{cite web|title=Iwata becomes CEO of Nintendo of America|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2013-04-24-iwata-becomes-ceo-of-nintendo-of-america|date=2013-04-24|last=Martin|first=Matt|work=GamesIndustry.biz|publisher=Gamer Network|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-12|archive-date=2017-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810212900/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2013-04-24-iwata-becomes-ceo-of-nintendo-of-america}}</ref><ref name="iwatadeath">{{cite press release|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/pdf/2015/150713.pdf|title=代表取締役社長の逝去および異動に関するお知らせ(訃報)|publisher=任天堂|access-date=2015-07-13|date=2015-07-12|dead-url=no|language=ja}}</ref>。担任美国任天堂首席执行官后他宣布不再在[[E3电子娱乐展|E3电子娱乐展]]上召开大型新闻发布会，而是舉辦一些每一場都會針對特定人士的小型活動<ref>{{cite web|title=No Nintendo Press Conference at E3 2013|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/04/25/no-nintendo-press-conference-at-e3-2013|date=2013-04-23|last=Goldfarb|first=Andrew|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|publisher=Ziff Davis|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150611020826/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/04/25/no-nintendo-press-conference-at-e3-2013|archive-date=2015-06-11}}</ref>。在2013年后半年在[[东京都|东京]]旅游时，岩田聰构思了一种能够与任天堂游戏进行联动的实体玩具。这个想法很快便在不到一年的时间内变成了[[Amiibo|Amiibo]]实体[[手办|-{zh-cn:手办;zh-hk:首辦;zh-tw:人形模型;}-]]，并正式发售。Amiibo取得了商业成功，发售大约一个月便在全球卖出了600万个<ref name="Time2015">{{cite magazine|last=Peckham|first=Matt|date=2015-03-18|title=Exclusive: Inside Nintendo's Bold Plan to Stay Vibrant for the Next 125 Years|url=http://time.com/3749061/nintendo-mobile-gaming/|dead-url=no|magazine=[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]|language=en|publisher=[[时代公司|时代公司]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428122714/http://time.com/3749061/nintendo-mobile-gaming/|archive-date=2015-04-28|access-date=2015-07-21}}</ref>。2015年任天堂又发售了Amiibo卡片，截至2016年3月，二者的合计销量超过了6400万个，为任天堂的所有游戏平台都带去了正面的商业影响<ref>{{cite web|title=|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/events/160428/03.html|author=[[君岛达己|君岛达己]]|date=2016-04-28|publisher=任天堂|language=ja|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-03-18|page=3|script-title=ja:2016年4月28日（木） 決算説明会}}</ref>。<!-- 6400万个需要计算得到，符合[[WP:日常计算|WP:日常计算]]规定。见该页的第四张幻灯片。2014财年手办卖了1050万个；2015财年手办卖了2470万个，卡片卖了2890万个。三者加起来6410万。 -->

