早在2010年上半年，[[苹果公司|苹果公司]]的[[App_Store_(iOS/iPadOS)|App Store]]的成功让游戏开发者们担心市场的重心会倒向[[智能设备|智能设备]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Nintendo not concerned about competition from Apple|url=https://www.engadget.com/2010/03/04/nintendo-not-concerned-about-competition-from-apple/|date=2010-03-04|last=Rawson|first=Chris|work=[[Engadget|Engadget]]|publisher=[[美国在线|美国在线]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-09-03|archive-date=2017-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170925040043/https://www.engadget.com/2010/03/04/nintendo-not-concerned-about-competition-from-apple/}}</ref>。当年7月，岩田聰承认了任天堂与苹果公司之间的竞争关系，并将其看作「未来的敌人」<ref>{{cite news|first=Bianca|last=Bosker|newspaper=[[赫芬顿邮报|赫芬顿邮报]]|publisher=[[美国在线|美国在线]]|date=2010-07-07|access-date=2010-09-03|title=Satoru Iwata, Nintendo CEO: Apple is the 'enemy of the future'|url=https://www.huffpost.com/entry/satoru-iwata-nintendo-ceo_n_568045|archive-date=2019-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190705222225/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/satoru-iwata-nintendo-ceo_n_568045|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。不过，在莅年的一次采访中，岩田聰坚决反对任天堂进军手机游戏市场，称一旦这么做，任天堂将「不再是任天堂」<ref>{{cite web|title=Nintendo + Smartphones? Iwata Says "Absolutely Not"|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/09/14/nintendo-smartphones-iwata-says-absolutely-not|date=2011-09-13|last=Thomas|first=Lucas M.|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|publisher=Ziff Davis|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-09-03|archive-date=2017-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730121534/http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/09/14/nintendo-smartphones-iwata-says-absolutely-not}}</ref>。他认为手机平台会为了盈利而不顾手机游戏的质量，不过随着手机游戏市场的持续发展，他的观点也在慢慢转变<ref name="Mobileturn">{{cite web|title=The history behind Nintendo's flip-flop on mobile gaming|url=https://www.engadget.com/2015/03/17/nintendo-mobile-iwata/|date=2015-03-17|last=Gilbert|first=Ben|work=[[Engadget|Engadget]]|publisher=[[美国在线|美国在线]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-09-03|archive-date=2017-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170925035847/https://www.engadget.com/2015/03/17/nintendo-mobile-iwata/}}</ref>。在2012年，他承认智能手机给任天堂带来了巨大的挑战，但是仍然对任天堂的能力充满信心<ref>{{cite web|title=Unintimidated by Apple, Nintendo's Boss Says the World Still Needs Dedicated Gaming Handhelds|url=http://kotaku.com/5936557/unintimidated-by-apple-nintendos-boss-says-the-world-still-needs-dedicated-gaming-handhelds|date=2012-08-21|last=Totilo|first=Stephen|work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|publisher=Gawker Media|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-09-03|archive-date=2017-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170925132133/https://kotaku.com/5936557/unintimidated-by-apple-nintendos-boss-says-the-world-still-needs-dedicated-gaming-handhelds}}</ref>。在2013财年的一封致股东公开信中，岩田聰说：「……我相信人们只在专用游戏设备上玩游戏的时代已经结束了。」<ref name="2013QaA"/>他认为智能手机可以为用户提供快速娱乐，而一些曾使用过专用游戏设备的领域在智能设备下会更有未来<ref name="2013QaA">{{cite web|title=2013年10月31日（木） 第2四半期決算説明会 質疑応答|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/events/131031qa/index.html|date=2013-10-31|publisher=任天堂|language=ja|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-03-11}}</ref>。分析师和投资者不断要求岩田聰改变主意，不过他仍然坚持不进军手机游戏市场，招致外界批评<ref name="stubborn"/>。Architect Grand Design公司<!--アーキテクトグランドデザイン株式会社-->的社长豐崎禎久根据任天堂常年忽视外界反馈的历史指出，任天堂「无法接触」<ref name="WSJ011714"/>。这最终也在某种程度上影响了任天堂的收入和声望<ref>{{cite news|newspaper=[[日本時報|日本時報]]|date=2015-07-21|access-date=2015-09-03|title=The man who revolutionized gaming|url=http://www.japantimes.co.jp/opinion/2015/07/21/editorials/the-man-who-revolutionized-gaming/|archive-date=2015-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150731085757/http://www.japantimes.co.jp/opinion/2015/07/21/editorials/the-man-who-revolutionized-gaming/|dead-url=no|language=en|subscription=yes}}</ref>。

2015年3月，随着传统游戏硬件市场开始萎缩，岩田聰将任天堂的经营重心分出一部分放在了正在成长的[[手机游戏|手机游戏]]市场，与手机游戏开发商[[DeNA|DeNA]]达成合作协议，开发手机游戏<ref name="ap"/><ref>{{cite magazine|last=Peckham|first=Matt|date=2015-03-18|title=Exclusive: Nintendo CEO Reveals Plans for Smartphones|url=http://time.com/3748920/nintendo-mobile-games/|dead-url=no|magazine=[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]|language=en|publisher=[[时代公司|时代公司]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150423091350/http://time.com/3748920/nintendo-mobile-games/|archive-date=2015-04-23|access-date=2015-07-13}}</ref>。这与任天堂以前专注于开发[[独占游戏|独占游戏]]以吸引客户购买他们的硬件的经营模型有着巨大的不同<ref>{{cite web|title=Nintendo explains why Mario is not on smartphones|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-explains-why-mario-is-not-on-smartphones/1100-6415851/|date=2013-10-30|last=Makuch|first=Eddie|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS互動]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-21|archive-date=2014-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140310031606/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-explains-why-mario-is-not-on-smartphones/1100-6415851/}}</ref>。岩田聰强调，尽管任天堂的[[知识产权|知识产权]]会登陆手机平台，任天堂不会损害它们的价值。他还强调任天堂的主要目标是拓展任天堂的用户群体，而不是多赚钱。这与Wii开辟蓝海的路线类似<ref>{{cite web|title=Players More Important Than Money, Nintendo Pres. Says About Smartphone Deal|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/players-more-important-than-money-nintendo-pres-sa/1100-6426003/|date=2015-03-18|last=Makuch|first=Eddie|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS互動]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-21|archive-date=2017-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729002851/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/players-more-important-than-money-nintendo-pres-sa/1100-6426003/}}</ref>。在与DeNA达成合作协议后，他重申了他对[[网络游戏免费模式|免费游玩]]游戏的态度。他将这类游戏称为「免费进入」游戏<ref>{{cite web|url=https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=92538|title=任天堂社長岩田聰表示免費遊戲正在扼殺自家電玩硬體事業|author=William|website=巴哈姆特電玩資訊站|date=2014-02-05|accessdate=2021-03-10|language=zh-tw}}</ref>，可能会在未来对市场上的游戏质量造成威胁。{{failed verification|他认为尽管这样的游戏会在短期内起到有效的宣传作用，这种游戏模式已经过时，对游戏开发有害}}<ref name="Mobileturn"/><ref>{{cite magazine|last=Peckham|first=Matt|date=2015-03-23|title=8 More Fascinating Things Nintendo CEO Satoru Iwata Told Time|url=http://time.com/3747342/nintendo-ceo-satoru-iwata/|dead-url=no|magazine=[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]|language=en|publisher=[[时代公司|时代公司]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150401124358/http://time.com/3747342/nintendo-ceo-satoru-iwata/|archive-date=2015-04-01|access-date=2015-09-20}}</ref>。他还强调[[轉蛋|轉蛋]]的商业模型与任天堂的核心价值观不合，不能用来构建「任天堂与顾客之间的长久纽带」<ref>{{cite magazine|author=Nakamura|first=Yuji|date=2017-02-02|title=Nintendo Plays With Fire|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-02-02/nintendo-plays-with-fire|dead-url=no|magazine=Bloomberg Business|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170902092908/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-02-02/nintendo-plays-with-fire|archive-date=2017-09-02|access-date=2017-02-05}}</ref>。

在生命的最后几个月，岩田聰担任[[任天堂Switch|任天堂Switch]]的首席开发者，监督了该游戏机的开发过程。在2017年2月一次与《[[時代雜誌|时代]]》杂志的采访中，宫本茂认为岩田聰对这款游戏机的目标是将其设计成便携以促进人们之间的交流。岩田聰则在其中专注于机器的技术问题<ref>{{cite web|title=Satoru Iwata Put Lots Of Thought Into The Nintendo Switch, Says Miyamoto|url=http://kotaku.com/satoru-iwata-put-lots-of-thought-into-the-nintendo-swit-1792378208|date=2017-02-15|last=Ashcraft|first=Brian|work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|publisher=Gawker Media|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2017-03-18|archive-date=2017-02-15|archive-url=https://archive.is/20170215191423/http://kotaku.com/satoru-iwata-put-lots-of-thought-into-the-nintendo-swit-1792378208}}</ref>。

==== 公众关系 ====
{{see also|社长问|任天堂直面会}}
<!-- 檔案不存在 [[File:Satoru_Iwata_E3_2012_holding_bananas.jpg|thumb]]上播放的任天堂直面会视频中，他在面朝观众之前先静静地盯着手上的香蕉几秒钟<ref name="kotaku banana"/>|链接=Special:FilePath/Satoru_Iwata_E3_2012_holding_bananas.jpg]] ，可從英文維基百科取得 -->
在就任任天堂社长后的前几年，岩田聰为了将更多经历投入在编程上，直到新硬件公布之前他都很少在媒体前露面<ref group="書" name="Hasegawa2010"/>{{rp|46}}。不过，他对在公众前露面的态度发生了改变，最终成为了任天堂公众关系的重要一部分。岩田聰通过社交媒体与粉丝互动，改善了任天堂与粉丝之间的关系<ref name="time why mattered"/>。他还在2006年9月开设了「社长问」访谈系列，分享他对任天堂的雇员、游戏和硬件的见解<ref name="wired"/>。拥有游戏程序员背景的岩田聰经常对其他开发者的观念模式感兴趣，从而催生了这个系列<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/corporate/links/|year=2015|publisher=任天堂|language=ja|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-22|script-title=ja:社長が訊く リンク集|archive-date=2015-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723075625/http://www.nintendo.co.jp/corporate/links/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=社長が訊く『ニンテンドー3DS』ソフトメーカークリエーター 篇|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/3ds/interview/creators/intro/index.html|author=岩田聪|year=2011|publisher=任天堂|language=ja|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-03-11|series=社长问}}</ref>。这些访谈中大量穿插着岩田聰与其他员工之间的插科打诨，被认为展现了岩田聰与员工之间良好的情谊<ref name="nytimes"/>。这些访谈还涉及了任天堂内部的工作情况，被认为展现了一贯神秘的任天堂开放的一面<ref>{{Cite podcast|url=https://soundcloud.com/analyseasia/episode-50-a-tribute-to-satoru-iwata-nintnedos-future-with-serkan-toto|title=Episode 50: A Tribute To Satoru Iwata & Nintnedo's Future With Serkan Toto|website=Tech in Asia|accessdate=2020-03-12|via=SoundCloud|publisher=Tech in Asia|series=Analyse Asia|time=05:36|date=2015-08-15|first1=Bernard|last1=Leong|first2=Serkan|last2=Toto|language=en}}</ref>。

2011年，岩田聰开设了[[任天堂直面会|任天堂直面会]]。与行业通用的信息发布方式不同，[[任天堂直面会|任天堂直面会]]向全部公众公开，以在线发布会形式发布任天堂的新游戏和新产品<ref name="time why mattered"/>。这些视频同样风趣幽默，与岩田聰本人的性格相符<ref name="Eurogamer"/>。这与索尼和微软一贯严肃的形象天差地别<ref name="ArsTech0713"/>。例如，在一段任天堂直面会视频中，岩田聰与时任美国任天堂总裁[[雷吉·菲尔斯-埃米|雷吉·菲尔斯-埃米]]动手格斗，以宣布[[Mii|Mii]]（玩家的[[头像|头像]]）会在《[[任天堂明星大亂鬥3DS/Wii_U|任天堂明星大亂鬥3DS/Wii U]]》中登场<ref name="time why mattered"/><ref>{{cite web|title=You can import your Mii to fight in the next Super Smash Bros.|url=http://www.polygon.com/e3-2014/2014/6/10/5792076/super-smash-bros-wii-u-mii-fighter|date=2014-06-10|last=Corriea|first=Alexa Ray|work=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|publisher=[[沃克斯传媒|沃克斯传媒]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-19|archive-date=2017-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170824093119/https://www.polygon.com/e3-2014/2014/6/10/5792076/super-smash-bros-wii-u-mii-fighter}}</ref>。社长问和任天堂直面会经常催生[[網路迷因|網路迷因]]：例如岩田聰在宣布坏消息时经常使用的「请理解」短句、在论坛帖子中加入社长问中经常出现的「[岩田笑]」字样，以及在2012年[[E3电子娱乐展|E3电子娱乐展]]上为宣传[[大金刚系列|大金刚系列]]新作而出现的岩田聰盯着香蕉的画面<ref name="Guardian0713"/><ref name="kotaku banana">{{cite web|title=Nintendo Proves There's Nothing as Bananas as Holding ... Bananas|url=http://kotaku.com/5916119/nintendo-proves-theres-nothing-as-bananas-as-holdingbananas|date=2012-06-06|last=Ashcraft|first=Brian|work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|publisher=Gawker Media|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-19|archive-date=2015-11-16|archive-url=https://archive.is/20151116000242/http://kotaku.com/5916119/nintendo-proves-theres-nothing-as-bananas-as-holdingbananas}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first=Tiffany|last=Ap|work=[[CNN|CNN]]|publisher=[[透納廣播公司|透納廣播公司]]|date=2015-07-13|access-date=2015-07-19|title=Fans mourn death of Nintendo President Satoru Iwata|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/07/13/world/nintendo-ceo/|archive-date=2017-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170824051905/http://www.cnn.com/2015/07/13/world/nintendo-ceo/|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-33505823|title=Nintendo's Satoru Iwata: Gamers pay tribute|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2015-07-13|access-date=2015-09-01|archive-date=2015-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150910184813/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-33505823|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。

社长问和任天堂直面会让岩田聰成为了任天堂的形象代言人<ref name="ArsTech0713">{{cite news|first=Mark|last=Walton|newspaper=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|publisher=[[康泰纳仕|康泰纳仕]]|date=2015-07-13|access-date=2015-07-31|title=Without Iwata, what does the future hold for Nintendo?|url=https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2015/07/without-iwata-what-does-the-future-hold-for-nintendo/|archive-date=2017-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106080708/https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2015/07/without-iwata-what-does-the-future-hold-for-nintendo/|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。岩田聰也喜欢与记者交流，甚至提前准备有趣的小故事。就算时间紧迫，他也会与记者闲聊<ref name="FavoriteGame">{{cite magazine|last=Chikushi|first=Yuji|year=2015|title=Iwata-san, What is Your Favorite Game? A reporter's reflection of the late Nintendo CEO's personality|url=http://ignition.co/315|dead-url=yes|magazine=東洋經濟|language=en|publisher=[[東洋經濟新報社|東洋經濟新報社]]|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6aoRLVLD4?url=http://ignition.co/315|archive-date=2015-08-16|access-date=2015-08-15}}</ref>。

==== 其他项目 ====
岩田聰分别在1995年和1998年协助[[石原恆和|石原恆和]]成立了[[Creatures|Creatures]]和[[宝可梦公司|宝可梦公司]]<ref>{{cite interview|publisher=任天堂|date=2009-09-04|access-date=2015-07-12|series=社长问|page=1|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/interview/ipkj/vol1/index.html|dead-url=no|script-title=ja:社長が訊く 『ポケットモンスター　ハートゴールド・ソウルシルバー』|language=ja|author1=森本茂树|author2=石原恒和|interviewer=岩田聪}}</ref><ref name="IA-HG3"/>。岩田聰后来又在宝可梦公司独立成立时协调处理了日本内外授权变更的事宜<ref name="IA-HG3"/>。1998年6月6日，岩田聰帮助他的同事及挚友[[糸井重里|糸井重里]]创立了{{Link-ja|HOBO日刊ITOI新闻|ほぼ日刊イトイ新聞}}，并担任其“电脑部长”。糸井重里在该公司成立前一个月请求岩田聰设计网页并负责解决技术问题，岩田聰同意了，并被任命为“电脑部长”。岩田聰认为这份职务很有趣，一直到2007年他全职在任天堂担任社长的时候都保留着这个职位<ref>{{cite interview|interviewer=[[糸井重里|糸井重里]]|work=1101.com|date=2007-09-10|publisher=ほぼ日刊イトイ新聞|page=11|language=en, ja|access-date=2015-07-16|url=http://www.1101.com/iwata/2007-09-14.html|archive-date=2015-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150821062125/http://www.1101.com/iwata/2007-09-14.html|dead-url=no|author=岩田聪|script-title=ja:電脳部長回顧録}}</ref>。在被提拔为任天堂社长后，他的编程热情依然不减，在上任后不久便把自己分配到HAL研究所的一个开发团队中开发GameCube游戏《[[任天堂明星大乱斗DX|任天堂明星大乱斗DX]]》<ref name="BBC0713"/><ref name="GDC2005"/>。除了脑锻炼系列外，他还协助出品了诸如《[[汉字直输_DS乐引辞典|汉字直输 DS乐引辞典]]》、《[[英语苦手之大人的DS_英语训练|英语苦手之大人的DS 英语训练]]》以及《[[监修_日本常识力检定协会_事到如今难以启齿_大人的常识力锻炼DS|监修 日本常识力检定协会 事到如今难以启齿 大人的常识力锻炼DS]]》<span style="color:red">'''（你们名字短一点会死吗？）'''</span>在内的教育类游戏<ref group="書" name="Inoue2009"/>{{rp|91}}。他还参与了[[动物森友会系列|动物森友会系列]]、[[马力欧系列|马力欧系列]]、[[銀河戰士系列|銀河戰士系列]]、[[薩爾達傳說系列|薩爾達傳說系列]]以及其他系列的开发工作<ref name="IGNprofile"/><ref name="rolling stone">{{cite magazine|last=Kreps|first=Daniel|date=2015-07-13|title=Satoru Iwata, President and CEO of Nintendo, Dead at 55|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/culture/news/satoru-iwata-president-and-ceo-of-nintendo-dead-at-55-20150713|dead-url=no|magazine=[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石]]|language=en|publisher=Wenner Media|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150715191827/http://www.rollingstone.com/culture/news/satoru-iwata-president-and-ceo-of-nintendo-dead-at-55-20150713|archive-date=2015-07-15|access-date=2015-07-13}}</ref>。另外，岩田聰亦有在《[[舞動壞利歐工坊|手舞足蹈瓦力欧制造]]》<!--TODO:处理这个条目的转换词（尤其是标题）的问题，建立好重定向之后，争取把这个管道符删了-->中客串出場<ref>{{cite magazine|last=Parkin|first=Simon|date=2015-07-13|title=Postscript: Satoru Iwata (1959–2015)|url=http://www.newyorker.com/tech/elements/postscript-satoru-iwata-nintendo-president|dead-url=no|magazine=[[紐約客|紐約客]]|language=en|publisher=[[康泰纳仕|康泰纳仕]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150713222034/http://www.newyorker.com/tech/elements/postscript-satoru-iwata-nintendo-president|archive-date=2015-07-13|access-date=2015-07-13}}</ref>。自2013年开始，岩田聰还参与了[[增强现实|增强现实]]手机游戏《[[精灵宝可梦GO|精灵宝可梦GO]]》的开发。该游戏在岩田聰去世两个月后的2015年9月正式发布<ref>{{cite news|first=Chris|last=Morris|work=[[NBC新聞|NBC新聞]]|date=2015-09-11|access-date=2015-09-11|title=Pokémon leads Nintendo's mobile charge|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/tech/tech-news/pokemon-leads-nintendos-mobile-charge-n425706|archive-date=2017-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924141250/https://www.nbcnews.com/tech/tech-news/pokemon-leads-nintendos-mobile-charge-n425706|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first=Elaine|last=Kurtenbach|agency=[[美联社|美联社]]|newspaper=Financial Post|publisher=Postmedia Network|date=2015-09-11|access-date=2015-09-11|title=Pokemon Go for iOS, Android devices will allow players to bring 'pocket monsters' into the real world|url=http://business.financialpost.com/fp-tech-desk/post-arcade/pokemon-go-for-ios-android-devices-will-allow-players-to-bring-pocket-monsters-into-the-real-world|archive-date=2015-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150912204340/http://business.financialpost.com/fp-tech-desk/post-arcade/pokemon-go-for-ios-android-devices-will-allow-players-to-bring-pocket-monsters-into-the-real-world|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。

=== 疾病与逝世 ===
[[File:Satoru_Iwata_Nintendo_World_Store_memorial.jpg|thumb]]旗舰店设立的一片纪念区域中，粉丝们为岩田聰献上画有马力欧、星之卡比、塞尔达传说等任天堂经典游戏系列的纪念品与画作|alt=参见配图文字]]
在2014年6月5日，任天堂宣布岩田聰因身体原因将缺席2014年[[E3电子娱乐展|E3电子娱乐展]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Nintendo President Not Coming to E3 on Doctor's Advice|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-president-not-coming-to-e3-on-doctor-s-advice/1100-6420132/|date=2014-06-05|last=Makuch|first=Eddie|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS互動]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-18|archive-date=2015-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150523083447/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-president-not-coming-to-e3-on-doctor-s-advice/1100-6420132/}}</ref>。同年6月24日，岩田聰向股东发出公开信，称自己在一次常规身体检查中于[[膽管|膽管]]发现了一颗[[肿瘤|肿瘤]]，并在已在前一周的手术中摘除<ref name="rolling stone"/><ref>{{cite conference|publisher=任天堂|date=2014-06-24|access-date=2021-03-12|conference=第74期 定時株主総会|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/stock/meeting/140627/index.html|type=备忘录|dead-url=no|script-title=株主の皆様へ|author=岩田聪|language=ja}}</ref>。手术成功后，岩田聰花了大约四个月的时间恢复身体，并在10月回到公司上班。他的体重在此期间显著下降，但他称自己感觉更健康了<ref>{{cite web|title=Nintendo President Satoru Iwata returns to work after surgery|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/gaming/news/a606681/nintendo-president-satoru-iwata-returns-to-work-after-surgery.html|date=2014-10-29|last=Martin|first=Liam|work=[[數碼間諜|數碼間諜]]|publisher=[[赫斯特国际集团|赫斯特国际集团]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-18|archive-date=2015-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721200944/http://www.digitalspy.com/gaming/news/a606681/nintendo-president-satoru-iwata-returns-to-work-after-surgery.html}}</ref>。岩田聰随后在11月5日的任天堂直面会中首次公开露面，但是看上去「面容憔悴、脸色苍白」<ref>{{cite web|title=Nintendo's Iwata Addresses Concerns Over Rapid Weight Loss|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendos-iwata-addresses-concerns-over-rapid-weig/1100-6423401/|date=2014-11-06|last=Crossley|first=Rob|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS互動]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-18|archive-date=2015-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706110459/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendos-iwata-addresses-concerns-over-rapid-weig/1100-6423401/}}</ref>。他从容地接受了这个变化，在2015年6月更新了自己的Mii形象，新形象的体型更瘦小<ref>{{cite tweet|author=岩田聰|user=Nintendo|number=609514061475115008|date=2015-06-12|access-date=2015-07-18|title=|language=ja|script-title=ja:[岩田]私は、昨年６月に病気で手術をした影響で少しスリムになりました。退院後、体重はほとんど変わっておらず、この体型が維持できそうですので、公式Miiを現状に合わせることにしました。よろしくお願いします。#Iwatter}}</ref>。2015年1月28日，岩田聰突发高烧，被怀疑患上[[流感|流感]]，股东会议也相应推迟<ref>{{cite tweet|author=岩田聰|user=Nintendo|number=560599759946145792|date=2015-01-28|access-date=2015-07-18|script-title=ja:[岩田] 本日、アナリストおよび投資家様を対象とした第3四半期決算説明会の開催を予定しておりましたが、昨夜より発熱がありインフルエンザの疑いがあるため、大変申し訳ございませんが開催を延期させていただくことにいたしました。変更後の日程は改めてお知らせさせていただきます。|language=ja}}</ref>。在同年6月26日参加了另一场股东会议后，岩田聰再次病倒入院<ref name="Polygon0717">{{cite web|title=Nintendo releases Genyo Takeda's memorial address for Satoru Iwata|url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/7/17/8996339/satoru-iwata-eulogy-genyo-takeda-nintendo|date=2015-07-17|last=McWhertor|first=Michael|work=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|publisher=[[沃克斯传媒|沃克斯传媒]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-18|archive-date=2017-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906125929/https://www.polygon.com/2015/7/17/8996339/satoru-iwata-eulogy-genyo-takeda-nintendo}}</ref><ref name="NL081516">{{cite web|title=Satoru Iwata Offered Pokémon GO Feedback From His Hospital Bed|url=http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2016/08/satoru_iwata_offered_pokemon_go_feedback_from_his_hospital_bed|date=2016-08-15|last=McFerran|first=Damien|language=en|dead-url=no|website=[[Nintendo_Life|Nintendo Life]]|access-date=2017-02-02|archive-date=2017-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170927000936/http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2016/08/satoru_iwata_offered_pokemon_go_feedback_from_his_hospital_bed}}</ref>。就算在病房中，他依旧使用笔记本电脑继续工作，给石原恒和提供《精灵宝可梦GO》的反馈<ref name="NL081516"/>。2015年7月11日，岩田聰因胆管癌[[併發症|併發症]]去世，享年55岁。任天堂在7月13日公布了他的死讯<ref name="iwatadeath"/>。

在7月13日，任天堂总部[[半旗|降半旗]]为他默哀<ref name="flag"/>。任天堂北美分公司也在同日在社交媒体上沉默一天以示默哀<ref>{{cite news|first=Saira|last=Mueller|work=[[国际财经时报|国际财经时报]]|publisher=IBT Media|date=2015-07-13|access-date=2015-07-13|title=Gaming industry pays tribute to Nintendo CEO Satoru Iwata, dead at 55|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/gaming-industry-pays-tribute-nintendo-ceo-satoru-iwata-dead-55-2005560|archive-date=2015-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150714024604/http://www.ibtimes.com/gaming-industry-pays-tribute-nintendo-ceo-satoru-iwata-dead-55-2005560|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。游戏业界的从业人士以及玩家均在社交媒体上表达了他们的沉痛心情，同时也感谢他做出的成就<ref name="flag">{{cite web|title=The Video Game Community Pays Tribute to Satoru Iwata|url=http://kotaku.com/the-video-game-community-pays-tribute-to-satoru-iwata-1717397315|date=2015-07-12|last=Plunkett|first=Luke|work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|publisher=Gawker Media|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-12|archive-date=2015-07-13|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150713063708/http://kotaku.com/the-video-game-community-pays-tribute-to-satoru-iwata-1717397315}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Nintendo fans pay tribute to Satoru Iwata|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/trending/nintendo-fans-pay-tribute-to-satoru-iwata-1.3149239|date=2015-07-13|last=Bowman|first=John|publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|加拿大廣播公司]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-13|archive-date=2015-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150714184728/http://www.cbc.ca/news/trending/nintendo-fans-pay-tribute-to-satoru-iwata-1.3149239}}</ref>。粉丝们在全球各地设立纪念场所，例如位于[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]的[[日本駐俄羅斯大使館|日本駐俄羅斯大使館]]，以及位于[[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]]的[[紐約任天堂|紐約任天堂]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Russian Nintendo Fans Honor Satoru Iwata at the Japanese Embassy|url=http://kotaku.com/russian-nintendo-fans-honor-satoru-iwata-at-the-japanes-1717927760|date=2015-07-15|last=Ashcraft|first=Brian|work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|publisher=Gawker Media|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-19|archive-date=2015-07-15|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150715102750/http://kotaku.com/russian-nintendo-fans-honor-satoru-iwata-at-the-japanes-1717927760}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Satoru Iwata Memorial at the Nintendo World Store in NYC|url=http://irl.kotaku.com/satoru-iwata-memorial-at-the-nintendo-world-store-in-ny-1718206441|date=2015-07-16|last=Totilo|first=Stephen|work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|publisher=Gawker Media|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-19|archive-date=2015-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150719012206/http://irl.kotaku.com/satoru-iwata-memorial-at-the-nintendo-world-store-in-ny-1718206441}}</ref>。[[索尼電腦娛樂全球工作室|索尼電腦娛樂全球工作室]]董事長[[吉田修平|吉田修平]]得悉岩田聰的死後表示：「他為遊戲產業的發展做出了巨大的貢獻，願岩田先生能夠安息」<ref>{{Cite tweet|author=[[吉田修平|吉田修平]]|user=yosp|number=620388345969971200|date=2015-07-12|script-title=ja:ゲーム業界の発展に多大な貢献をされた岩田さんのご冥福をお祈りします。|language=ja}}</ref>。而以負責精灵宝可梦系列音效創作闻名的作曲家[[增田順一|增田順一]]則发推文表示：「他是宝可梦的理解者之一，同時也是一個偉大的領袖。前幾天我探訪他的時候他還很精神……由衷希望他能夠安息」<ref>{{Cite tweet|author=[[增田順一|增田順一]]|user=Junichi_Masuda|number=620396563240628225|date=2015-07-12|script-title=ja:任天堂の岩田社長が逝去されました。ポケモンの理解者であり、素晴らしいリーダーでした。先日お会いした時はお元気だったのに。。心よりご冥福をお祈り致します|language=ja}}</ref>。他的母校東京工業大學在8月4日发表了一篇追忆文章，包含了他以前的同班同学和教授对他的回忆<ref name="TokyoITAug4"/>。在2015年[[游戏大奖|游戏大奖]]的颁奖典礼上，雷吉·菲尔斯-埃米向他致敬，称他「无所畏惧」、「在各种意义上都非常独特」<ref>{{cite web|title=Watch The Game Awards pay tribute to Satoru Iwata|url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/12/3/9847012/the-game-awards-satoru-iwata-tribute|date=2015-12-03|last=Farokhmanesh|first=Megan|work=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|publisher=[[沃克斯传媒|沃克斯传媒]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-12-09|archive-date=2015-12-04|archive-url=https://archive.is/20151204033020/http://www.polygon.com/2015/12/3/9847012/the-game-awards-satoru-iwata-tribute}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Reggie Fils-Aime pays tribute to late Nintendo president Satoru Iwata|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-12-04-reggie-fils-aime-pays-tribute-to-late-nintendo-president-satoru-iwata|date=2015-12-04|last=Philips|first=Tom|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|publisher=Gamer Network|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-12-09|archive-date=2017-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170902094517/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-12-04-reggie-fils-aime-pays-tribute-to-late-nintendo-president-satoru-iwata}}</ref>。

在公布岩田聰死讯的几个小时后，有人拍摄到任天堂在京都的总部上方出现了一道彩虹。这张照片在上传到[[Twitter|Twitter]]后被大量转发。人们根据[[瑪利歐賽車系列|瑪利歐賽車系列]]中的“彩虹之路”赛道，将其命名为「通往天堂的彩虹之路」<ref>{{cite news|last1=Sola|first1=Katie|title=As the world mourns CEO Iwata's passing, a rainbow rises over Nintendo headquarters|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/07/13/nintendo-iwata_n_7786560.html|access-date=2015-07-14|newspaper=[[赫芬顿邮报|赫芬顿邮报]]|publisher=[[美国在线|美国在线]]|date=2015-07-13|archive-date=2015-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150714094936/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/07/13/nintendo-iwata_n_7786560.html|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Molloy|first1=Mark|title=Satoru Iwata: Rainbow 'road' appears above Nintendo HQ after CEO's death|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/nintendo/11737283/Satoru-Iwata-Rainbow-road-appears-above-Nintendo-HQ-after-CEOs-death.html|access-date=2015-07-14|newspaper=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]|publisher=[[電訊媒體集團|電訊媒體集團]]|date=2015-07-13|archive-date=2015-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150715025901/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/nintendo/11737283/Satoru-Iwata-Rainbow-road-appears-above-Nintendo-HQ-after-CEOs-death.html|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。任天堂依日本佛教传统为岩田聰举办了葬礼，在7月16-17日于京都举行。尽管受到了[[颱風浪卡_(2015年)|-{zh:颱風浪卡; zh-cn:超强台风浪卡; zh-hk:超強颱風浪卡; zh-mo:颱風浪卡; zh-tw:強烈颱風南卡;}-]]的影响，仍有约4100人冒着暴风雨献上敬意<ref>{{cite news|first=Takashi|last=Mochizuki|newspaper=[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]|publisher=[[道琼斯公司|道琼斯公司]]|date=2015-07-17|access-date=2015-07-17|title=Fans remember Nintendo President Iwata at funeral|url=https://blogs.wsj.com/japanrealtime/2015/07/17/fans-remember-nintendo-president-iwata-at-funeral/|archive-date=2015-07-24|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150724043448/http://blogs.wsj.com/japanrealtime/2015/07/17/fans-remember-nintendo-president-iwata-at-funeral/|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Thousands Attend Two-Day Funeral for Satoru Iwata|url=http://kotaku.com/thousands-attend-two-day-funeral-for-satoru-iwata-1718506891|date=2015-07-17|last=Schreier|first=Jason|work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|publisher=Gawker Media|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-17|archive-date=2017-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171002021808/https://kotaku.com/thousands-attend-two-day-funeral-for-satoru-iwata-1718506891}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Thousands attend Iwata's funeral in Kyoto|url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/7/17/8988549/thousands-attend-iwatas-funeral-in-kyoto|date=2015-07-17|last=Crecente|first=Brian|work=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|publisher=[[沃克斯传媒|沃克斯传媒]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-17|archive-date=2015-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150719221658/http://www.polygon.com/2015/7/17/8988549/thousands-attend-iwatas-funeral-in-kyoto}}</ref>。{{link-ja|通夜|通夜}}过后，岩田聰的遗体被[[火化|火化]]，{{fact|骨灰被安葬在京都某处，具体位置没有公开}}<ref name="0730Kotaku">{{cite web|title=''Smash Bros.'' Creator Talks of Satoru Iwata's Funeral|url=http://kotaku.com/smash-bros-creator-talks-of-satoru-iwatas-funeral-1721024061|date=2015-07-30|last=Nakamura|first=Toshi|work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|publisher=Gawker Media|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-07-31|archive-date=2015-07-31|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150731122246/http://kotaku.com/smash-bros-creator-talks-of-satoru-iwatas-funeral-1721024061}}</ref>。<!-- 应该还要去检查周刊Fami通的那一期，itoi的专栏，具体而言大概是 周刊Fami通 2015年8月13日号 左右 https://bookwalker.jp/de1db7023c-6b50-4f06-bb32-b33f55614a7b/ -->

岩田聰去世后，時任任天堂[[代表董事|代表董事]]宮本茂與竹田玄洋共同臨時代理社長職務<ref name="CNNMoneycitesNactingpresidents">{{cite news|url=https://money.cnn.com/2015/07/12/technology/nintendo-president-satoru-iwata-dead/index.html|title=Nintendo President Satoru Iwata dies at 55|work=CNN Money|publisher=[[时代华纳|时代华纳]]|date=2015-07-12|access-date=2015-07-15|first=Charles|last=Riley|archive-date=2015-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150714040628/http://money.cnn.com/2015/07/12/technology/nintendo-president-satoru-iwata-dead/index.html|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。同年9月14日，任天堂宣布其人力资源管理部部长、前美国任天堂首席执行官[[君岛达己|君岛达己]]将继任为第五任社长<ref name="personnel change">{{cite press release|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/pdf/2015/150914.pdf|date=2015-09-14|access-date=2021-03-12|publisher=任天堂|dead-url=no|script-title=ja:代表取締役の異動および役員の委嘱・管掌・担当変更に関するお知らせ|language=ja}}</ref>。

== 影響 ==
{{Rquote|right|text=在我的名片上，寫著我的頭銜叫公司社長。而在我腦中，我是一個遊戲開發者。但是在我心裡，我一直是個遊戲玩家。|author=岩田聰|source=在2005年遊戲開發者大會上的{{le|主題演講|Keynote}}<ref name="GDC2005">{{cite web|title=GDC 2005: Iwata Keynote Transcript|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2005/03/11/gdc-2005-iwata-keynote-transcript|date=2005-03-10|last=Casamassina|first=Matt|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|publisher=Ziff Davis|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-08-15|archive-date=2015-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150814045055/http://www.ign.com/articles/2005/03/11/gdc-2005-iwata-keynote-transcript}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Video: Satoru Iwata's 'Heart Of A Gamer' keynote at GDC 2005|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/248404/Video_Satoru_Iwatas_Heart_Of_A_Gamer_keynote_at_GDC_2005.php|author=Staff|date=2015-07-13|work=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|publisher=UBM plc|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2016-07-13|archive-date=2016-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160719150459/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/248404/Video_Satoru_Iwatas_Heart_Of_A_Gamer_keynote_at_GDC_2005.php}}</ref>}}
在他的一生中，岩田聰以他不同寻常的想法以及改变电子游戏的表现形式而闻名<ref name="Eurogamer"/><ref name="Legacy">{{cite news|last=Hiranand|first=Ravi|work=[[CNN|CNN]]|publisher=[[透納廣播公司|透納廣播公司]]|date=2015-07-13|access-date=2015-09-02|title=Nintendo's CEO Satoru Iwata played by his own rules|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/07/13/tech/nintendo-ceo-satoru-iwata-legacy/|archive-date=2016-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160215122233/http://www.cnn.com/2015/07/13/tech/nintendo-ceo-satoru-iwata-legacy/|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。他被视作任天堂的化身：富有童趣、诙谐幽默、古灵精怪<ref>{{cite magazine|last=Rundle|first=Michael|date=2015-07-13|title=Nintendo President Satoru Iwata dies at 55|url=https://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2015-07/13/nintendo-president-satoru-iwata-dead|dead-url=no|magazine=[[连线|连线]]|language=en|publisher=[[康泰纳仕|康泰纳仕]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150912103258/http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2015-07/13/nintendo-president-satoru-iwata-dead|archive-date=2015-09-12|access-date=2015-09-02}}</ref>。他娴熟的编程能力让他被视为「天才程式設計師」，有人甚至将他称为「日本的[[比尔·盖茨|比尔·盖茨]]」<ref name="TokyoITAug4"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://japanese.engadget.com/2015/08/07/Iwacchi-ftw/|date=2015-08-08|last=Tane|first=Kiyoshi|work=[[Engadget|Engadget]]日本|publisher=[[美国在线|美国在线]]|language=ja|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-10-08|script-title=ja:追悼・岩田聡氏。ゲームで辿る天才プログラマの軌跡 (1. 初期ファミコン編)|archive-date=2015-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151009011235/http://japanese.engadget.com/2015/08/07/iwacchi-ftw/}}</ref>。他亲力亲为，获得了开发者和玩家的喜爱与尊敬<ref name="Eurogamer"/>。他在2005年游戏开发者大会的开幕演讲《玩家之心》被视为道出了他的心声——一位热爱电子游戏的商人<ref group="書" name="Inoue2009"/>{{rp|63}}。他以及包括宫本茂在内的其他任天堂员工被看作扩大游戏市场、开辟全新游戏类型的大功臣<ref group="書" name="Jones2012"/>{{rp|53}}<ref group="書" name="Hasegawa2010"/>{{rp|51}}。通过针对不同市场的方式，岩田聰避免了与索尼和微软直接竞争，成功达成了他的目标<ref name="Eurogamer"/><ref name="Legacy"/>。相应的，他被称为「温和的革命者」<ref name="Eurogamer"/>，任天堂DS和Wii的朴素硬件成功地扩张了市场<ref name="Eurogamer"/>。《[[连线_(杂志)|连线]]》杂志的克里斯·科勒（{{lang-en|Chris Kohler}}）面对任天堂DS和Wii推出后游戏玩家群体数量激增的场景，说：「感谢任天堂的岩田聰先生，现在我们都是游戏玩家了」<ref>{{cite magazine|last=Kohler|first=Chris|date=2015-07-16|title=Thanks to Nintendo's Satoru Iwata, We're All Gamers Now|url=https://www.wired.com/2015/07/satoru-iwata-gamer/|dead-url=no|magazine=[[连线|连线]]|language=en|publisher=[[康泰纳仕|康泰纳仕]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150730065229/http://www.wired.com/2015/07/satoru-iwata-gamer|archive-date=2015-07-30|access-date=2015-07-31}}</ref>。不过，尽管受到了广泛的尊重，他坚持不让任天堂进军手机游戏市场的行为招致了批评<ref name="stubborn">{{cite news|first=Harumi|last=Ozawa|agency=[[法新社|法新社]]|work=雅虎科技|publisher=[[雅虎|雅虎]]|date=2015-07-13|access-date=2015-09-02|title=Nintendo CEO Satoru Iwata dies of cancer at 55|url=https://www.yahoo.com/tech/s/nintendo-says-ceo-satoru-iwata-died-cancer-55-005136382.html?nf=1|archive-date=2015-09-03|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6bFuRaBa9?url=https://www.yahoo.com/tech/s/nintendo-says-ceo-satoru-iwata-died-cancer-55-005136382.html?nf=1|dead-url=yes|language=en}}</ref>。岩田聰离世后，雷吉·菲尔斯-埃米评价他称，「……他对任天堂以及整个电子游戏市场的影响需要花费很多年才会被完全接受」<ref>{{cite news|last=Molina|first=Bret|newspaper=[[今日美國|今日美國]]|publisher=[[甘尼特|甘尼特]]|date=2015-07-13|access-date=2015-09-02|title=Nintendo CEO Satoru Iwata dies at 55|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/gaming/2015/07/12/nintendo-ceo-satoru-iwata-dies-55/30064255/|archive-date=2015-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150901065659/http://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/gaming/2015/07/12/nintendo-ceo-satoru-iwata-dies-55/30064255/|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。

2015年10月，有玩家制作了一个自制的岩田聰Mii形象的Amiibo，在[[eBay|eBay]]上拍出1,900美元的价格。拍卖所得收入全部捐献给了慈善机构{{le|Child's Play (慈善组织)|Child's Play (charity)|Child's Play}}，以资纪念<ref>{{cite web|title=One-of-a-Kind Satoru Iwata Memorial Amiibo on Sale to Raise Money for Charity|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/one-of-a-kind-satoru-iwata-memorial-amiibo-on-sale/1100-6431151/|date=2015-10-05|last=Hussein|first=Tamoor|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS互動]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2015-10-08|archive-date=2015-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007211424/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/one-of-a-kind-satoru-iwata-memorial-amiibo-on-sale/1100-6431151/}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first=Ben|last=Skipper|newspaper=[[国际财经时报|国际财经时报]]|publisher=IBT Media|date=2015-10-09|access-date=2015-10-09|title=Nintendo: Satoru Iwata Amiibo figure raises $1,900 for charity on eBay|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/nintendo-satoru-iwata-amiibo-figure-raises-1900-charity-ebay-1523219|archive-date=2015-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151011203609/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/nintendo-satoru-iwata-amiibo-figure-raises-1900-charity-ebay-1523219|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。在2015年[[金摇杆奖|金摇杆奖]]上，评委一致同意追授岩田聰「终身成就奖」，以表彰他对整个电子游戏行业的巨大影响<ref>{{cite news|first=Connor|last=Sheridan|work=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]|publisher=[[未來出版社|未來出版社]]|date=2015-10-30|access-date=2015-10-30|title=Satoru Iwata receives the Lifetime Achievement Award at the Golden Joysticks|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/satoru-iwata-lifetime-achievement-golden-joystick-awards/|archive-date=2015-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151031113542/http://www.gamesradar.com/satoru-iwata-lifetime-achievement-golden-joystick-awards/|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。在2016年[[D.I.C.E.大奖|D.I.C.E.大奖]]上，他同样被追授「终身成就奖」<ref>{{cite web|title=Satoru Iwata to be honoured with posthumous DICE Lifetime Achievement Award|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-01-13-satoru-iwata-to-be-honoured-with-posthumous-dice-lifetime-achievement-award|date=2016-01-13|last=Philips|first=Tom|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2016-01-13|archive-date=2016-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160115084538/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-01-13-satoru-iwata-to-be-honoured-with-posthumous-dice-lifetime-achievement-award}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=DICE honors Satoru Iwata with Lifetime Achievement Award|url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/2/18/11058084/dice-honors-satoru-iwata-with-lifetime-achievement-award|date=2016-02-18|last=Campbell|first=Colin|work=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|publisher=[[沃克斯传媒|沃克斯传媒]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2016-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160219153221/http://www.polygon.com/2016/2/18/11058084/dice-honors-satoru-iwata-with-lifetime-achievement-award|archive-date=2016-02-19}}</ref>。在2016年[[游戏开发者选择奖|游戏开发者选择奖]]上，游戏《[[时空幻境_(2008年游戏)|时空幻境]]》的美术设计师大卫·赫尔曼（{{lang-en|David Hellman}}）为他制作了一部动画短片纪念他<ref>{{cite web|title=Watch a touching tribute to deceased Nintendo CEO Satoru Iwata|url=https://www.theverge.com/2016/3/17/11251702/satoru-iwata-nintendo-ceo-tribute-video|date=2016-03-17|language=en|dead-url=no|last1=McCormick|first1=Rich|website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|access-date=2016-03-17|archive-date=2016-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160317062202/http://www.theverge.com/2016/3/17/11251702/satoru-iwata-nintendo-ceo-tribute-video}}</ref>。2019年7月，{{Link-ja|HOBO日刊ITOI新闻|ほぼ日刊イトイ新聞}}在日本出版了《岩田先生》（{{lang|ja|岩田さん}}）。该书由永田泰大编辑，收录了社长问采访，以及与宫本茂、糸井重里等好友在岩田聰死后的采访内容。在民众的强烈要求下，Hobonichi宣布与Tuttle-Mori Agency合作，共同将本书翻译成中英文等多国语言<ref>{{cite web|title=Publisher Of Satoru Iwata Book Says Unauthorized Translations Will Be Subject To Criminal Charges|url=https://kotaku.com/publisher-of-satoru-iwata-book-says-unauthorized-transl-1836904607|date=2019-08-02|last=Ashcraft|first=Brian|work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|publisher=Gawker Media|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2019-08-06|archive-date=2019-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190803133318/https://kotaku.com/publisher-of-satoru-iwata-book-says-unauthorized-transl-1836904607}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Publisher Of The Iwata Book Issues Warning To Fan Translators, Says English Version In The Works|url=https://www.thegamer.com/publisher-iwata-book-issues-warning-fan-translators-says-english-version-works/|date=2019-08-03|last=Baird|first=Scott|work=The Gamer|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2019-08-06|archive-date=2019-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190806235504/https://www.thegamer.com/publisher-iwata-book-issues-warning-fan-translators-says-english-version-works/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=有关Hobonichi出版，纪念岩田先生的新书《Iwata-san》的外文出版事宜|url=https://www.1101.com/books/iwatasan/index_en.html|accessdate=2021-03-12|author=ほぼ日刊イトイ新聞|language=en,zh,ja}}</ref>，[[碧日|碧日出版公司]]于2021年初在北美发行该书<ref>{{cite web|title=A Book Collecting Nintendo's "Iwata Asks" Interviews Is Coming Next Year|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/a-book-collecting-nintendos-iwata-asks-interviews-/1100-6480155/|date=2020-07-24|last=Petite|first=Steven|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-07-24|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725015431/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/a-book-collecting-nintendos-iwata-asks-interviews-/1100-6480155/}}</ref>；[[译文出版社|译文出版社]]则于2021年7月初在中国大陆发行该书。

=== 电子游戏中的致敬 ===
《[[星际火狐_零|星际火狐 零]]》的开发团队为了纪念岩田聰，在制作人员列表的末尾写上了「谨以本游戏献给我们在战斗中倒下的僚机飞行员」字样<ref>{{cite web|title=A touching Iwata tribute is in Star Fox Zero|url=http://www.destructoid.com/a-touching-iwata-tribute-is-in-star-fox-zero-354629.phtml|date=2016-04-11|last=Rowen|first=Nic|language=en|dead-url=no|website=[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]|access-date=2016-04-11|archive-date=2016-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412121728/http://www.destructoid.com/a-touching-iwata-tribute-is-in-star-fox-zero-354629.phtml}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first=Connor|last=Sheridan|work=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]|publisher=[[未來出版社|未來出版社]]|date=2016-04-11|access-date=2016-04-11|title=Watch Star Fox Zero's lovely tribute to Satoru Iwata|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/star-fox-zero-iwata-credits/|archive-date=2016-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160413224000/http://www.gamesradar.com/star-fox-zero-iwata-credits/|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。无独有偶，在2017年发行的任天堂Switch首发护航游戏《[[塞尔达传说_旷野之息|塞尔达传说 旷野之息]]》中，玩家发现游戏中的一位角色的样貌与岩田聰相似。该角色要求玩家前往附近的「萨托利山」寻找「山林霸主」，玩家发现「萨托利」与「聪」的发音类似，加上「山林霸主」在游戏中被视为引-{}-导神<!-- 英文维基百科的原文是 guiding spirit，能在游戏当中找到对应的翻译是最好的。目前这个翻译我觉得还可以润饰一下，有点感觉别扭 -->，认为这是开发团队向在游戏开发过程中离世的岩田聰的精心致敬<ref>{{cite web|title=Zelda: Breath of the Wild's alleged Iwata tribute is beautiful|url=http://www.polygon.com/2017/3/15/14937568/zelda-breath-of-the-wild-iwata-tribute|date=2017-03-15|last=Kuchera|first=Ben|work=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|publisher=[[沃克斯传媒|沃克斯传媒]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2017-03-18|archive-date=2017-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317202857/http://www.polygon.com/2017/3/15/14937568/zelda-breath-of-the-wild-iwata-tribute}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Zelda: Breath Of The Wild Easter Egg May Pay Tribute To Late Nintendo President Saturo Iwata|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/zelda-breath-of-the-wild-easter-egg-may-pay-tribut/1100-6448677/|date=2017-03-13|last=Dayus|first=Oscar|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS互動]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2017-03-18|archive-date=2017-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170319111547/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/zelda-breath-of-the-wild-easter-egg-may-pay-tribut/1100-6448677/}}</ref>。2017年9月，一群研究任天堂Switch系统软件的人员发现[[任天堂Switch系统软件|任天堂Switch系统软件]]中包含模拟器版本的红白机游戏《[[高尔夫_(游戏)|高尔夫]]》。该游戏的原版由岩田聰一人编写程序，而用户只要在系统时间设定在岩田聰去世的7月11日、手持Joy-Con控制器对着主界面摆出双手垂直向前的动作（其在任天堂直面会中的招牌动作）便可触发该[[彩蛋_(媒体)|彩蛋]]<ref>{{cite web|title=The Golf game on every Nintendo Switch is actually a tribute to late Satoru Iwata|url=https://www.vg247.com/2017/09/20/the-golf-game-on-every-nintendo-switch-is-actually-a-tribute-to-late-satoru-iwata/|date=2017-09-20|last=Saed|first=Sherif|work=[[VG247|VG247]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2017-09-20|archive-date=2017-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170921002202/https://www.vg247.com/2017/09/20/the-golf-game-on-every-nintendo-switch-is-actually-a-tribute-to-late-satoru-iwata/}}</ref>。任天堂不久后移除了这个彩蛋<ref>{{cite web|title=Switch's hidden Iwata tribute removed in latest update|url=https://www.polygon.com/2017/12/27/16822340/nintendo-switch-golf-game-hidden-removed|date=2017-12-27|last=Frank|first=Allegra|work=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2017-12-27|archive-date=2017-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171228054142/https://www.polygon.com/2017/12/27/16822340/nintendo-switch-golf-game-hidden-removed}}</ref>。在《[[精灵宝可梦_究极之日／究极之月|精灵宝可梦 究极之日／究极之月]]》中，玩家若携带《[[精靈寶可夢_金·銀|精靈寶可夢 金·銀]]》中首次登场的宝可梦踏入Game Freak大楼，便会有非玩家角色提及多亏了一个“很厉害的家伙”<!-- 需要玩过这个游戏的编者确认原文是如何翻译的，简繁都要 -->他们才得以将所有数据存放在一张[[Game_Boy_Color|Game Boy Color]]游戏卡中。这指的是岩田聰在开发《[[精靈寶可夢_金·銀|精靈寶可夢 金·銀]]》所编写的压缩算法让开发团队得以在维持金·銀的世界规模的同时将《[[精靈寶可夢_紅·綠|精靈寶可夢 紅·綠]]》的所有内容加入其中<ref>{{cite web|title=Pokemon Ultra Sun & Moon features a nice salute to Satoru Iwata|url=https://www.destructoid.com/pokemon-ultra-sun-moon-features-a-nice-salute-to-satoru-iwata-474242.phtml|date=2017-11-23|last=Moyse|first=Chris|work=[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2017-11-23|archive-date=2018-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180911161010/https://www.destructoid.com/pokemon-ultra-sun-moon-features-a-nice-salute-to-satoru-iwata-474242.phtml}}</ref>。

